-- Fernandez to Leave Argentina Hospital Today After Thyroid Cancer Operation
-- B y   N a t h a n   G i l l
-- 2012-01-07T14:27:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-07/fernandez-to-leave-argentina-hospital-today-after-thyroid-cancer-operation.html
Argentina ’s President  Cristina
Fernandez de Kirchner  will be released from a hospital today
after successfully undergoing surgery for thyroid cancer.  Fernandez, who began her second, four-year term on Dec. 10,
is recovering without complications after surgeons removed her
thyroid gland on Jan. 4, according to a statement published
today on the president’s website. She will travel Olivos where
she will remain on medical leave until Jan. 24, the statement
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sylvia Wier at 
 swier@bloomberg.net  